        {
            "id": 5931172,
            "title": "中國銀河(06881)料首季純利升最多90%至31億元人幣",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社9日專訊》中國銀河(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06881-HK</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:601881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/601881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">601881-CN</a>)公布,於今年首季,預計純利27.73億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>至31億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>,按年增長70%至90%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　公司稱,純利增加由於主動把握市場機遇,穩中求進,不斷尋求業務突破,公司財富管理、投資交易、投資銀行等業務均實現較大幅度增長,取得較好經營業績。(rh)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5931172",
